  "Because physical oceanography studies fish anatomy": "",
  "Because the current is a physical phenomenon, while tuna migration is a biological behavior influenced by that current": "",
  "Because both disciplines focus exclusively on the chemistry of seawater": "",
  "Because bluefin tuna are only found in geological formations on the seafloor": "",
  "The Gulf Stream is a major ocean current (physical oceanography), and tuna migration is a biological behavior. Understanding how physical conditions in the ocean affect marine life requires collaboration between these two disciplines.": ""
